**  MSG
E-01 REVERSING INSTRUCTION IS <G / Z / S / A>
E-02 REVERSING INSTRUCTION IS <1 2>
E-03 REVERSING INSTRUCTION IS <S K>
E-04 REVERSING PROCESS NO. IS NUMBER BETWEEN <1-15>
E-05 THE PROCESS OR DEPT THAT REVERSING INPUT EITHER OF THEM
E-06 PROCESS NO. THAT REVERSING  IS NOT RECIEPT
E-07 INPUT PREVIOUS<PROCESS  DEPARTMENT>
E-08 REVERSING PROCESS IS NOT IN PROCESS NAME M/F
E-09 REVERSING SECTION IS NOT IN DETAILS M/F
E-10 REVERSING PLACE IS <Y N>
E-11 LOC ORDER INT PROCESS CAN'T INPUT FROM PROCESS-2 TO 15
E-12 LOC ORDER INT PROCESS <N>
